  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add the sliced almonds and cook, stirring occasionally, for 4 minutes or until lightly browned.",
    "add the onion, garlic, and bell pepper and cook, stirring occasionally, for 4 minutes or until the vegetables are tender.",
    "add the almond butter, infused oil, salt, black pepper, and cayenne pepper and stir until well combined.",
    "cook for an additional 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "scoop the mixture onto a talavera plate and sprinkle with chopped parsley if desired.",
    "serve warm or at room temperature."
